------- FILE finalgame.dasm LEVEL 1 PASS 2
      1  10000 ????						; Notes:
      2  10000 ????						; 1. [FIXED] Obstacle no longer spawns immediately - 2 second delay
      3  10000 ????						; 2. [FIXED] Replaced missile with ball object - no more scanline shifting
      4  10000 ????						; 3. [FIXED] Ball uses 2-frame spawn hide to avoid wrong position on first frame
      5  10000 ????						; 4. [FIXED] Sprite boundary clamping tightened to prevent edge stretching
      6  10000 ????						; 5. [FIXED] Score now increments once per second (60-frame counter)
      7  10000 ????						; 6. keep idea of collecting objects around the screen, perhaps give a
      8  10000 ????						;    timer (shown by them flashing) and if the player fails to collect
      9  10000 ????						;    them they lose a life?
     10  10000 ????						; Next steps:
     11  10000 ????						; 1. [DONE] add delay to obstacle spawn
     12  10000 ????						; 2. add lives to player, and make the player lose lives when they are hit
     13  10000 ????						;    by a projectile
     14  10000 ????						; 3. add some kind of background to the game
     15  10000 ????						; 4. [DONE] change points from per frame to per second (NTSC = ~60fps)
     16  10000 ????						;------------------------------------------------
